# **Flower Delivery Philippines - Send bouquets of flowers to Manila**

FlowerStore.ph is the best-rated online gift shop and flower delivery in the Philippines. Delivering specially crafted [flower bouquets](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-bouquet) and [gift boxes](https://flowerstore.ph/search/keepsake-gifts/gift-boxes) to your loved ones all over Metro Manila, Metro Cebu, Davao City, and over 50 other cities with FREE same-day delivery. We also provide FREE nationwide shipping on selected products.

Show your love and appreciation by sending gifts and fresh flowers to your loved ones. We have over a hundred expertly designed and beautifully hand-crafted fresh flower arrangements made by the best florists in the Philippines, and gift items to choose from and perfect for any occasion such as [anniversaries](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/anniversary), [romantic occasions](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/romance), [birthdays](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/birthday), [grand openings/inaugurals](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/inaugurals-and-grand-openings), [birth of a new baby](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/new-baby-and-kids-gifts), [funerals and condolences,](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/funeral-flowers) [Mother's Day](https://flowerstore.ph/campaign/mothers-day), [Father's Day](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/fathers-day), [Valentine's](https://flowerstore.ph/campaign/valentines "Valentine's") and many more.

As the #1 Flower Delivery service in the Philippines, FlowerStore.ph also has the perfect gifts and [bouquet of flowers](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-bouquet "floral arrangements") for saying [Sorry](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/i-am-sorry), [Get Well Soon](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/get-well), [Congratulations](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/Congratulations), [Thanks](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/thank-you), or even [Just Because](https://flowerstore.ph/search/occasions/just-because).

### [Flower Delivery Metro Manila](https://flowerstore.ph/)

The vast choices found in FlowerStore.ph's online gift shop can pair you up with the perfect type of gift for any person in your life. Whether it's your family, friends, or coworkers, there will surely be a gift for them. Gift and flower delivery in Metro Manila is made easy with FlowerStore.ph's same-day delivery option. Get free same-day delivery to your office or even right at your doorstep.

Within Metro Manila, our selected areas with express delivery service are: Makati, Taguig, Quezon City, Pasig, Pasay, Mandaluyong and Marikina.

### [Flower Delivery Cebu](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/send-flowers-cebu)

Looking to give a bouquet to a special someone miles away? We've got you covered.

From Metro Manila, we are now bringing our expertly crafted floral bouquets and arrangements to Cebu! Gift and flower delivery to Cebu has never been easier with FlowerStore.ph's expert delivery services. Explore an online store with hundreds of gifts and arrangements specially made for several occasions.

Looking for a [flower shop near you](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-shop-near-me "flower shop near you")? FlowerStore.ph offers free same-day delivery of expertly crafted flower arrangements to over 50 cities in the Philippines.

Looking for a reliable [flower shop in Quezon City](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-shop-quezon-city "flower shop in Quezon City")? Look no further than FlowerStore.ph. Our fast and easy online ordering process ensures your loved ones receive the perfect gift on time.

### [Send Flowers and Gifts to the Philippines](https://flowerstore.ph/)

Away from Home? No Problem!

Send flowers and gifts to the Philippines easily with FlowerStore.ph. Whether it is a small or large [bouquet](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-bouquet) or even a special gift package, FlowerStore.ph has got you covered. Trust your special surprises to your loved ones in the Philippines with FlowerStore.ph's professional gift and flower delivery services. Your family or significant other will surely feel your love even though you are oceans away.

## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs):

**What does a bouquet of flowers typically consist of?**

A [bouquet of flowers](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-bouquet) is an artful arrangement of various blooms, often mixed with foliage, designed to convey a specific sentiment or enhance a space's aesthetic.

**How do I choose the perfect flower bouquet?**

Consider the recipient's preferences, the occasion, and the intended message when choosing a [flower bouquet](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-bouquet). Each bloom carries its own meaning, contributing to the overall sentiment.

**Where can I find a reliable [flower shop near me](https://flowerstore.ph/collection/flower-shop-near-me)?**

FlowerStore.ph is a reputable online flower shop near you, offering a wide range of beautifully crafted bouquets for various occasions.

